Source: rdf-fdw
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), libcurl4-openssl-dev (>= 7), libxml2-dev (>= 2.5.0), pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/jimjonesbr/rdf_fdw

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-rdf-fdw
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-rdf-fdw
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: RDF triplestore foreign data wrapper for PostgreSQL
  rdf_fdw is a PostgreSQL foreign data wrapper for RDF triplestores exposed
  through SPARQL endpoints.
